fields.name: Zoomer
fields.description: Zoomer is an application designed to encourage ride-sharing among the e-bike, e-scooter community. Starting out as. a side-project during my first few years working as Tech Inc. I realized that many people were buying e-transport vehicles and then leaving them regularly unused. This is a community project designed to help make the world green! Let me know what you think!
